sequenceDiagram
participant Client
participant API
participant Facade as HBnBFacade
participant UserRepo
participant Place
participant PlaceRepo
participant DB

Client->>API: POST /places (place data)
API->>Facade: create_place(user_id, data)
Facade->>UserRepo: get_by_id(user_id)
UserRepo->>DB: SELECT user
DB-->>UserRepo: user found
Facade->>Place: new Place(data)
Facade->>PlaceRepo: save(place)
PlaceRepo->>DB: INSERT place
DB-->>PlaceRepo: OK
PlaceRepo-->>Facade: place saved
Facade-->>API: success
API-->>Client: 201 Created
